              ${reset}${blackf}|               |               |               |               |${reset}
   ${redf}‚Ėą     ‚Ėą${reset}    ${blackf}|${reset}    ${greenf}‚Ėą     ‚Ėą${reset}    ${blackf}|${reset}    ${yellowf}‚Ėą     ‚Ėą${reset}    ${blackf}|${reset}    ${bluef}‚Ėą     ‚Ėą${reset}    ${blackf}|${reset}    ${purplef}‚Ėą     ‚Ėą${reset}    ${blackf}|${reset}    ${cyanf}‚Ėą     ‚Ėą${reset}
