 ${reset}${redf}  ‚Ėą‚Ėą${boldon}${redfbright}‚Ėą‚Ėą${boldoff}${redf}‚Ėą‚Ėą   ${reset}${greenf}   ‚Ėą‚Ėą${boldon}${greenfbright}‚Ėą‚Ėą${boldoff}${greenf}‚Ėą‚Ėą   ${reset}${yellowf}   ‚Ėą‚Ėą${boldon}${yellowfbright}‚Ėą‚Ėą${boldoff}${yellowf}‚Ėą‚Ėą   ${reset}${bluef}   ‚Ėą‚Ėą${boldon}${bluefbright}‚Ėą‚Ėą${boldoff}${bluef}‚Ėą‚Ėą ${reset}${purplef}     ‚Ėą‚Ėą${boldon}${purplefbright}‚Ėą‚Ėą${boldoff}${purplef}‚Ėą‚Ėą   ${reset}${cyanf}   ‚Ėą‚Ėą${boldon}${cyanfbright}‚Ėą‚Ėą${boldoff}${cyanf}‚Ėą‚Ėą   ${reset}
